    },
    {
      "type": "other",
      "text": "Sworn to and subscribed before me on this 31st day of August in the year 1867, and I hereby certify that I know the affiants to be credible witnesses, and that they reside as stated in the foregoing joint affidavit. I also certify that said affidavit was read over to and understood by them, before they signed the same. I also certify that I am entirely disinterested in this matter.",
